long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: To-Doist for Click Up, is a task manager made on the API's for Click Up. Main features include having track of your spaces, teams, folders and tasks. CRUD operations for tasks on Click Up have been implemented. So have a go at managing your tasks without having to visit Click Up. All you need to do is connect your Workspaces.
